<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 12:28:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：雷诺（Geely），雷诺（Renault）关于销售的会谈，巴西的制造交易，消息人士称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/geely-renault-talks-over-sales-manufacturing-deals-brazil-sources-say-2025-02-12/</link><description>三位消息人士称，法国汽车制造商雷诺（Renault）及其中国合伙人吉利（Geely.ul）计划在本月晚些时候宣布一项协议，以扩大全球贸易战，以寻求新的增长市场，以扩大新的增长市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 12:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/geely-renault-talks-over-sales-manufacturing-deals-brazil-sources-say-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国制裁链，伊朗，俄罗斯油在油轮上，推动原油成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-sanctions-strand-iran-russia-oil-tankers-driving-up-crude-costs-2025-02-12/</link><description>贸易资料和分析师说，随着严厉的美国制裁减少了买家的数量，在船上持有的俄罗斯和伊朗石油数量达到了多个月的高点，而贸易资料和分析师说，较少的油轮可用于运送货物并提高原油成本。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:58:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-sanctions-strand-iran-russia-oil-tankers-driving-up-crude-costs-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>Google的首席执行官Pichai说，中国的DeepSeek做得很好</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/googles-ceo-pichai-says-chinas-deepseek-has-done-very-good-work-2025-02-12/</link><description>Alphabet首席执行官Sundar Pichai说，中国初创公司DeepSeek做得很好，表明了全球人工智能的程度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:57:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/googles-ceo-pichai-says-chinas-deepseek-has-done-very-good-work-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>美洲平静下降，因为通货膨胀，关税解析</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-12/</link><description>看看美国和迈克·多兰（Mike Dolan）的全球市场的前一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:17:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>部长说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-weighs-temporary-tax-cheap-chinese-steel-import-minister-says-2025-02-12/</link><description>钢铁部长HD Kumaraswamy说，印度可能会在六个月内对中国的钢铁征收15％-25％的临时税，这是由于廉价进口商的“严重挑战”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 10:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-weighs-temporary-tax-cheap-chinese-steel-import-minister-says-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>爱沙尼亚说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-aids-russian-drone-production-with-smuggled-western-parts-says-estonia-2025-02-12/</link><description>爱沙尼亚的外国情报公司在周三发表的年度国家安全报告中说，中国正在通过成为莫斯科武装部队的关键西方部件的枢纽，帮助俄罗斯的军事无人机生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 09:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-aids-russian-drone-production-with-smuggled-western-parts-says-estonia-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国说，武汉研究所没有参与创建Covid-19病毒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-wuhan-institute-was-not-involved-creating-covid-19-virus-2025-02-12/</link><description>中国外交部发言人在周三的常规新闻发布会上说，武汉病毒学研究所没有参与Covid-19病毒的创建或泄漏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 07:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-wuhan-institute-was-not-involved-creating-covid-19-virus-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军事眼睛更多的升级，包括“梦想”潜艇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-military-eyes-more-upgrades-including-dream-submarines-2025-02-12/</link><description>武装部队周三表示，菲律宾正在寻求购买更多的军事硬件，以使其武器库现代化，包括来自印度的额外的婆罗门导弹和至少两艘潜艇。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 07:15:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-military-eyes-more-upgrades-including-dream-submarines-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>咨询公司说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-purchases-chipmaking-equipment-decline-2025-consultancy-says-2025-02-12/</link><description>咨询公司周三表示，随着三年的增长，中国购买芯片制造设备将在今年下降，因为该行业努力应对产能的过度并面临美国制裁的限制。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 06:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-purchases-chipmaking-equipment-decline-2025-consultancy-says-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官说，扩建服务公司DKSH将受益于中国的关税。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/expansion-service-provider-dksh-meets-2024-profit-expectations-2025-02-12/</link><description>其首席执行官在周三的新闻发布会上表示，瑞士扩张服务提供商DKSH预计将受益于中国的新关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 06:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/expansion-service-provider-dksh-meets-2024-profit-expectations-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普可能会在1930年推出贸易歧视法，以支持美国互惠关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-may-dust-off-1930-trade-discrimination-law-back-reciprocal-us-tariffs-2025-02-12/</link><description>该法律受到威胁但从未征收关税的法律，仅在记录中出现。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 06:11:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-may-dust-off-1930-trade-discrimination-law-back-reciprocal-us-tariffs-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>台湾的富士康说，它可以计划围绕特朗普关税的生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-it-can-plan-production-around-trump-tariffs-2025-02-12/</link><description>该公司董事长周三表示，台湾最大的合同电子制造商和苹果的主要iPhone Maker的富士康可以计划其围绕美国新关税的生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 05:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-it-can-plan-production-around-trump-tariffs-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国国家资助的股票复兴计划是天空中的派吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/is-chinas-state-funded-stock-revival-plan-pie-sky-2025-02-12/</link><description>当中国指导其大型金融机构以帮助恢复和重新平衡挣扎的股票市场时，分析师认为该计划中的优点，但持怀疑态度会刺激恢复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 05:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/is-chinas-state-funded-stock-revival-plan-pie-sky-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国在8万亿美元的小型银行业中的记录合并增加了未来的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-record-mergers-8-trillion-small-banking-sector-raises-future-risks-2025-02-12/</link><description>路透社对官方数据的审查显示，中国去年有史以来最大的农村银行合并浪潮，但分析人士说，北京为解决小型银行业的风险所做的努力可能最终在道路上造成更多问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 04:32:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-record-mergers-8-trillion-small-banking-sector-raises-future-risks-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>在日产和本田的600亿巨型交易中的崩溃之内</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/inside-collapse-nissan-hondas-60-billion-mega-deal-2025-02-12/</link><description>不合理，再加上本田管理层将日产的决策缓慢的态度结合在一起，帮助鱼雷交易将创造出世界上最大的汽车制造商之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 04:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/inside-collapse-nissan-hondas-60-billion-mega-deal-2025-02-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>